Class AbandonOperationWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.core.OperationWrapper<AbandonOperation>
      • org.opends.server.core.AbandonOperationWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, AbandonOperation, Operation

    public abstract class AbandonOperationWrapper
extends OperationWrapper<AbandonOperation>
implements AbandonOperation
    This abstract class wraps/decorates a given abandon operation. This class will be extended by sub-classes to enhance the functionality of the AbandonOperationBasis.
